{"id": "ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 77, "displayName": {"text": "ELOREA", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSd1ZGbHBaVk5OWlhsdGNrNVNaM2xSYjI5emJVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Worth a visit just for the views and free smells. Great little spot hidden in Ktown. Some really interesting scents, and thoughtful and delicious drinks to pair with it. The perfume itself smelled great and they do a good job with explaining the inspiration behind it.\n\nThe views are fantastic for the area, and they have a nice seating area outside to just chill.\n\nGet the Lychee drink, it's fantastic but takes a while. The coffee with soy sauce cold foam was also really good and unique. All of the drinks seemed interesting and fun and I'd go back just for the drinks.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Worth a visit just for the views and free smells. Great little spot hidden in Ktown. Some really interesting scents, and thoughtful and delicious drinks to pair with it. The perfume itself smelled great and they do a good job with explaining the inspiration behind it.\n\nThe views are fantastic for the area, and they have a nice seating area outside to just chill.\n\nGet the Lychee drink, it's fantastic but takes a while. The coffee with soy sauce cold foam was also really good and unique. All of the drinks seemed interesting and fun and I'd go back just for the drinks.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alex Y", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114837786933334423879/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNAAmy4joyC4PfI91blkyKP4EWoIgTk_TzHqTY6EVUSdEWMA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-16T07:37:44.761692282Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSd1ZGbHBaVk5OWlhsdGNrNVNaM2xSYjI5emJVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSd1ZGbHBaVk5OWlhsdGNrNVNaM2xSYjI5emJVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c745043fe397:0x1318a347b8a3cde2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOVVRFSkpWRTB3YlZabE1FeHJXV1ZpUTJSeGRHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Elorea is a must-visit spot in Koreatown. Everything here feels like stepping into Seoul — from the atmosphere to the beautifully curated interior design and display details. The drinks are definitely the highlight, inspired by perfume scents and presented in such a unique and creative way. It’s a perfect place for catching up with close friends, taking aesthetic photos, or picking up cute gifts and souvenirs. Such a stylish and memorable experience overall!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Elorea is a must-visit spot in Koreatown. Everything here feels like stepping into Seoul — from the atmosphere to the beautifully curated interior design and display details. The drinks are definitely the highlight, inspired by perfume scents and presented in such a unique and creative way. It’s a perfect place for catching up with close friends, taking aesthetic photos, or picking up cute gifts and souvenirs. Such a stylish and memorable experience overall!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tina Wan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103885505226199899619/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKqAQ9zUD5knKV-mof_9UQsGoEq_q0iwMkZBx2qVu0eHScq7gq=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-11T20:46:37.710653307Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOVVRFSkpWRTB3YlZabE1FeHJXV1ZpUTJSeGRHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOVVRFSkpWRTB3YlZabE1FeHJXV1ZpUTJSeGRHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c745043fe397:0x1318a347b8a3cde2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdFJWcFhPR05rV0hac1IzaGpRMEpsWW5WaFZHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had a lovely experience here. I wish I’d gotten the name of the gentleman that helped me and my friends, because he did an excellent job walking us through the different perfumes Elorea has to offer. He provided excellent customer service! I really appreciated that it never felt like he was trying to sell us anything, there was no pressure to buy, and he was honest about which scents he liked and which weren’t really his thing but might work for others. The building is gorgeous, as well as the rooftop sitting area, and the cafe drinks based off of scents were fun to choose from. My friends and I had a really nice time, we all love the scents we bought, and I would definitely recommend this place :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had a lovely experience here. I wish I’d gotten the name of the gentleman that helped me and my friends, because he did an excellent job walking us through the different perfumes Elorea has to offer. He provided excellent customer service! I really appreciated that it never felt like he was trying to sell us anything, there was no pressure to buy, and he was honest about which scents he liked and which weren’t really his thing but might work for others. The building is gorgeous, as well as the rooftop sitting area, and the cafe drinks based off of scents were fun to choose from. My friends and I had a really nice time, we all love the scents we bought, and I would definitely recommend this place :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Simaya Renee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111316930758451986017/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWAbmDyCOoFdKSUkJ4V0JQg0ev29gHjmplAdrcqb3nr9z9oGrA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-05T20:42:14.946601949Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdFJWcFhPR05rV0hac1IzaGpRMEpsWW5WaFZHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdFJWcFhPR05rV0hac1IzaGpRMEpsWW5WaFZHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c745043fe397:0x1318a347b8a3cde2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s0NWVqRTRkM290YzI1d1RITTRiRlJZV0hkQmRXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "This place feels much more about the overall atmosphere and experience than just the menu. Elorea is primarily a perfume house, but the attached café and rooftop space make it a unique spot to spend time, especially in Koreatown.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place feels much more about the overall atmosphere and experience than just the menu. Elorea is primarily a perfume house, but the attached café and rooftop space make it a unique spot to spend time, especially in Koreatown.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sneha Jain", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111985761449740233458/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCUDanyE6YY6yQFl1gjdUKkP02mYbOiGKrCT4hE6IFB_234Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-03T03:58:58.288292595Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s0NWVqRTRkM290YzI1d1RITTRiRlJZV0hkQmRXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s0NWVqRTRkM290YzI1d1RITTRiRlJZV0hkQmRXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c745043fe397:0x1318a347b8a3cde2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCdmRreDVaR3hoZG1rM1dGQmpNRkJCU0ZnM2RGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "One of the must visit places in LA. I enjoyed my time browsing and chatting with the staff. My partner bought some handcream. We sat there enjoying their curation of drinks! I had the best matcha in my life! The experience was phenomenal!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of the must visit places in LA. I enjoyed my time browsing and chatting with the staff. My partner bought some handcream. We sat there enjoying their curation of drinks! I had the best matcha in my life! The experience was phenomenal!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Larrend Lacuesta", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108408897319703970549/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVL7nhMLHKtBSIxR5Y0lJnIUx5Jp6tUTyxYx5OqA6jH3E3xXLu6=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-26T19:36:51.109125392Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCdmRreDVaR3hoZG1rM1dGQmpNRkJCU0ZnM2RGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCdmRreDVaR3hoZG1rM1dGQmpNRkJCU0ZnM2RGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c745043fe397:0x1318a347b8a3cde2"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJl-M_BEXHwoAR4s2juEejGBM/photos/AWCwydhntYiMVpkJgGY_WbcYan1m1vDLQDSBNljqc75bKKRokggl9GBlsFCqQh-Zy1LPxdOiWRaIRdUk0CYxGmSN4haXQJydvdsIPDnGUXdVEYMsNdqJ7UPG5-TEY5i4atwz5UtLPID-Q0OWGVlKYqDCVPjxnbHkyAfPZYYhHyZM8H_qjxOj5DlN0UJ_87v_XbarivifjjtiipPlVXplBmBhK_4zVKc11WQ3DtG4nEqnoYjsPrURn3cCn2chopCDsDbR0dGKyAqOU-05ZXSeb9t9Jmv5EY10g55y637eUWkiM6a3MT7CK24SReEP1l7C8wEFTX0YJvSqO61IC0R8aZLKAxXqvvKYwP1iVCKlT6qn0IrdiMOhUUK8XP14rq-DYMvJmPmZ-fPcfsI-ttm0pAtfV02OeA8rHz7xIdCGVUChQfn3PW4XiPE4qDEdtqcdqK63", "widthPx": 3024, "heightPx": 4032, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "ELOREA", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/110297355963471802515"